{
  "texts": [
    "They are represented as groups of two i.e.",
    "FST I-II (light skin tone), FST III-IV, and FST V-VI (dark skin tone).",
    "There are 208, 241, and 207 clinical images across the three groups respectively.",
    "The choice of this dataset enables us to evaluate GPT-4V's robustness to analyzing medical images of various skin tones.",
    "Beyond the fine-grained diagnostic labels, DDI also contains a label for malignancy or not, which we utilize in our downstream analysis."
  ]
}